                <list>
                    <label>4.</label>
                    <item>Desirable that publicity covering this initial program be released when
                        agreement signed.<note n="3" xml:id="d464fn3">The Department’s telegraphic
                            instruction 2732, December 30, not printed, forwarded the text of the
                            agreement which the Ambassador was authorized to sign (800.48
                            FAA/12–3047). For the text of the new agreement signed at Rome on
                            January 3, 1948, see Department of State, Treaties and Other
                            International Acts Series (<gloss target="#t_TIAS1">TIAS</gloss>) No.
                            167S, or 62 Stat. (pt. 2) 1807.</note> Send urgently substance ur press
                        release for use in preparation simultaneous release here on signature of
                        agreement.</item>
                    <pb facs="0774" n="756" xml:id="pg_756"/>
                    <label>5.</label>
                    <item>This message supplemental to request for publicity contained <gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 2678, Dec. 20, <gloss target="#t_Mefa1">Mefa</gloss> 1, on agreement itself.<note n="4" xml:id="d464fn4">This telegraphic instruction, not printed, forwarded to
                            Rome the initial draft of the proposed new agreement (800.48
                            FAA/12–2047).</note> Suggest single release covering (<hi rend="italic">a</hi>) agreement and purposes program as a whole (<hi rend="italic">b</hi>) initial portion program set forth para 3 above.</item>
                </list>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
